				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Yes, the counter is incremented no matter what the cause of the A12 line going from low to high (0 to 1). I've tested using auto-incrementing when reading $2007. Note that it somehow filters out the multiple transitions of A12 that occur during PPU rendering on each scanline (and not due to the 22 pf capacitor across the A12 line either, since I tried removing that once).</div>

