					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">is there any commerce game that do toggle the A12 line to trigger an irq?</div>
<br />
<br />The way to test this in an emulator is to "mark" the IRQ counter whenever the A12 line is toggled from 0 to 1 via PPU register writes, then log an occurrence if this marked counter value causes an IRQ. Anything which resets the counter would "unmark" it.</div>

